            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". And nothing could better suit St. Paul’s purpose, who would not lie under that scandal of endeavouring an apostacy from the Jewish religion, (for the gospel which he preached was but the substance and perfection of the law), or that he served or worshipped any other God than the God of Abraham. ",
